<inglise> "Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> "Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> For the purpose of this Directive, 'product' means all movables even if incorporated into another movable or into an immovable. 'Product' includes electricity." </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevas direktiivis t&auml;hendab "toode" k&otilde;iki vallasasju isegi juhul, kui need on &uuml;hendatud teise vallasasja v&otilde;i kinnisasjaga. "Toode" h&otilde;lmab elektrienergiat." </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> In Article 15, paragraph 1(a) shall be deleted. </inglise>
